    <ns0:task id="activity_hospitals_1" name="establish and maintain a standardized acute HF risk-stratification process (develop tools that can be used for multiple conditions including HF, apply consistently across all Ontario hospitals, use a common standardized risk stratification assessment tool or process in the ED to assist clinical decision making, and have a pathway or mechanism to transfer patients to a higher level provider) (Role: Ontario hospitals; Objects: standardized risk stratification tools and transfer pathway)">
      <ns0:incoming>Flow_1</ns0:incoming>
      <ns0:outgoing>Flow_36</ns0:outgoing>
